snippet.title: Sagaia (1991) [Game Boy Longplay]
snippet.description: Sagaia aka. Darius II (ダライアスII is originally a 1989 arcade video game developed by Taito. It is the direct sequel to the 1987 Darius. Game was later ported by Act Japan to Nintendo Game Boy in 1991.
